          "stepDescription": "Wash chicken well and cut into desired size. Also finely chop the the spinach. Keep it aside.",
          "stepImages": []
        },
        {
          "stepDescription": "In a pan, heat mustard oil. Add cumin and mustard seeds and allow it to splutter. Add grated ginger, garlic and green chillies. Saute for a minute.",
